This folder intentionally has no product images yet.
WALL_CLADDING product images are resolved from PDC at request time
(see lib/room-preview/product-resolver.ts), same as CARPET_TILE.
Do not add placeholder/fake images here — see AGENTS.md / IMPROVMENT task notes.
When real product photos are vendored locally, name each file
"<SKU>.jpg" (or .png/.webp) to match the codes in
data/room-preview/wall-cladding-sku-allowlist.json, then re-run
scripts/generate-qr-product-manifest.mjs to refresh the manifest from disk.
